### **Initial Substantial Holder Notice – Key Details**  

- **Substantial Holder**: First Sentier Investors (Australia) IM Ltd (ACN 114 194 311) & associates (Mitsubishi UFJ Financial Group)  
- **Date of Becoming Substantial Holder**: 01/08/2025  
- **Total Voting Power**: **5.01%** (7,337,115 ordinary shares)  
  - Includes **5,339,368 shares** (First Sentier Group & subsidiaries)  
  - Includes **1,997,747 shares** (MUFG ownership influence)  
- **Relevant Interests**: Control via investment mandates (Corporations Act 2001 provisions)  
- **Major Registered Holders**:  
  - Citibank N.A. Hong Kong  
  - JP Morgan Chase  
  - Northern Trust entities  

*No material transaction pricing or capital impact disclosed beyond stake acquisition.*
